Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Devil,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.81,0:00:03.14,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,How can he be this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:05.52,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,Amidst such despair,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:08.86,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,when others cling to each other, how can he \Nspeak of survival, as though it's a given?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.86,0:00:12.65,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,Why does this man's voice resonate \Nso strongly within me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:16.16,Default,G,0,0,0,,That thing will either disappear or \Nweaken when the sun hits it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:19.54,Default,G,0,0,0,,We just have to last until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.00,Default,G,0,0,0,,We're going to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.58,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,How can this man's voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:27.84,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,sound so reassuring to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:33.01,Title,Sign 0104,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,256)}Those Who Cling, Those Who Struggle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:13.07,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I hope it's not broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:20.03,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I have to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.45,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.75,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.17,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Is anyone out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.71,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Someone's out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:37.80,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:39.17,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I can't walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.38,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Please help...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:52.73,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.32,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,It was like a cattle stampede.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.61,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.28,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.28,0:03:01.03,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.07,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I've been watching from below.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.70,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,It looks like Elaine and the others are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.70,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.20,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.08,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to get sentimental.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:17.63,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:21.18,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I can't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.59,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.97,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I-I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.64,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Don't poke your head out, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.23,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,But what are you going to do, Luca?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.85,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:35.44,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.19,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm too scared to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.78,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.74,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I need you to stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.24,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.41,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Both of us won't fit in this barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.37,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Besides, who'd seal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:49.41,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:53.67,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Honestly, you're such a scaredy-cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.00,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:59.80,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,If nothing else, be a \Nproper scaredy-cat, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:03.22,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Keep quiet, and don't make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.60,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,You just might be the type \Nthat survives the longest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.81,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.15,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.74,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,{\fad(1,934)}Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.37,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Ever since that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.87,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,I've felt like I'm wandering \Nthrough an endless night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.79,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,But I had forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.53,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,That this world is a place\Nwhere the sun rises.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.18,Default,P,0,0,0,,The time has finally come to \Ndraw this secret sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:46.59,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Even just based on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.93,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,I have a big advantage compared to back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.48,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.27,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,There are too many to burn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.19,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,More and more keep showing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:09.24,Default,P,0,0,0,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:12.37,Default - italics,P,0,0,0,,Explosive Fire Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.16,Default,P,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.04,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Don't act dumb, you shitty bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.00,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I'll squash you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.25,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Anyway, what's up with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:25.38,Default,P,0,0,0,,It's the resentment of those who died \Nhere due to torture or epidemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.18,Default,P,0,0,0,,It's absorbing the emotions \Nof those engulfed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,continuing to expand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:32.85,Default,P,0,0,0,,It's full of their hatred \Nand desire for salvation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.02,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,If hate is all something like that takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.73,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,the whole world would've sunk \Ninto a cesspool by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:42.52,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Why is it just happening in Albion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.15,Default,P,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.62,Default,F,0,0,0,,This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.66,Default,F,0,0,0,,It should not be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:56.29,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,It's just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:05:58.67,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,It's like I'm in a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.71,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,Is this actually happening in reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.52,Default,G,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die, do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.90,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:26.32,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,He still stands and refuses to back down \Nin this overwhelming nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:29.28,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,In all of this, he is the only certainty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.49,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.03,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,It's coming in from behind, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.49,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Behind me, Lady Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.29,Default,F,0,0,0,,O-Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.45,Default,G,0,0,0,,Don't pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.42,Default,G,0,0,0,,If you pray, your hands are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:41.46,Default,G,0,0,0,,What's that you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.34,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.02,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:02.98,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,This is the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.11,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm going to get crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.32,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm dead! I'm dead!\NI'm dead! I'm going to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.74,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I can't stand it... Let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:09.90,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Let me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.53,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:18.79,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I might just die, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:25.34,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,But it's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.38,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'll die yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.30,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,The more scared I am, the more alive I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.09,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,The more blood I cough up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:36.01,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,the more I know that it's warm in my veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:38.14,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm going to try...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.23,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm going to try, Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:44.52,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,Being scared means that I want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.46,Default,P,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.11,Default - italics,P,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:40.87,Default - italics,P,0,0,0,,Both the living and dead. All the souls \Nhere are calling out for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.21,Default - Apostle,Egg,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:48.42,Default - Apostle,Egg,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything in my world \Nis one unified thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.46,Default - Apostle,Egg,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything desires me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:55.30,Default - Apostle,Egg,0,0,0,,{\i1}the world I will create, \Nand calls out for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:57.68,Default - Apostle,Egg,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything will be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:00.89,Default - Apostle,Egg,0,0,0,,{\i1}fulfilled by one voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.10,Default,P,0,0,0,,Singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:10.86,Default,P,0,0,0,,Guts, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:11.78,Default,G,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:14.86,Default,P,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:17.99,Default,P,0,0,0,,It's resonating with the voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:21.29,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:21.99,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.79,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,What is this agony coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:30.46,Default - Apostle,Blob,0,0,0,,Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:52.52,Default - Apostle,Egg,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, the light overflows...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.54,Default,G,0,0,0,,Griffith!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.13,Default,Devil,0,0,0,,There will be a pillar of fire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.68,Default,Devil,0,0,0,,where blind sheep gather on holy ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.68,Default,Devil,0,0,0,,The hour of Heaven's fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.14,Default,Devil,0,0,0,,It has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.30,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:07.68,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,The tower and the monsters \Nvanished overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.20,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Were we just having a bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.29,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.70,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Oh, the puffy lady's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.12,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:37.50,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm really alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.71,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Oh, where's Luca?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.76,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.71,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.26,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Find Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.22,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:47.38,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:50.35,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca jammed me into the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:52.77,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.10,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.35,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:56.52,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.10,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.10,0:11:59.15,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:01.27,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,How will we find her in all this rubble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.32,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I don't want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.44,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,No, Luca...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.11,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:12.12,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,O-O-Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.54,Default,P,0,0,0,,She said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:19.71,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,H-H-H-Hurry up... Get me out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:23.18,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I-I-I-I'm going to catch a chill!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.05,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.56,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I'm freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:33.35,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.98,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,You're so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.48,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,It was worth living for.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:55.54,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,They're Kushans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.54,0:12:57.58,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Why are they all the way out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.63,Default,P,0,0,0,,The guys from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.92,Default,Tapasa,0,0,0,,That is the {\i1}krishna sena{\i0} from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.92,0:13:09.34,Default,Tapasa,0,0,0,,Could he be the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.51,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.72,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,Yet just as the divine prophecy said,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.72,0:13:15.64,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,there was a calamity in this \Nland, and he appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:19.94,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,The one we seek must be \Namong them, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:22.10,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:25.07,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,If we don't get outta here after \Nall that, I'm calling bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.99,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,Capture them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.20,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,They must be alive, not unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.16,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,Specifically, don't go easy on the \Nman with the massive sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.79,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,Don't lower your guard until \Nyou've cut off his limbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:45.88,Default,P,0,0,0,,Killing blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:48.80,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Personal issues aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:53.68,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,I cannot think of a better man to have \Nat my side in such a circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:56.02,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Although, it may not amount to much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.26,Default,G,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:13:59.36,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:00.52,Default,Kushan,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.11,Default,Kushan,0,0,0,,If you make a single move, these women...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:02.98,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:07.70,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Taking women and children \Nas hostages? Barbarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.44,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Heretics,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.44,0:14:12.08,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,how dare you enter our holy \Nland and do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:12.82,Default,F,0,0,0,,Azan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.82,0:14:14.54,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,You're tough to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:17.33,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese, I am glad to see you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:18.12,Default,F,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.45,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,You, as well, Vice-commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:21.66,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,We can talk later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.88,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:27.38,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Things have taken a strange turn \Nin the short time I was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.17,Default,G,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.48,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.48,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Hey, not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:43.48,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-Bada?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:50.07,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Is this the continuation of last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.61,0:14:54.33,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Nothing can surprise me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.70,Default,G,0,0,0,,Zodd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:57.08,Default - italics,G,0,0,0,,Why is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.50,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,How monstrous...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:05.54,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,This isn't the time to be impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.84,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,If we're to escape, it must be now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.17,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:09.75,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Everyone, stay together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.30,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,We'll storm through this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:39.62,Default - italics,Narr,0,0,0,,In that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:43.58,Default - italics,Narr,0,0,0,,all held their breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.62,Default - italics,Narr,0,0,0,,And all were transfixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.88,Default,G,0,0,0,,Griffith...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:04.40,Default - italics,Narr,0,0,0,,And all realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:07.94,Default - italics,Narr,0,0,0,,That what they had desired had come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.96,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,All of you, seize that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.41,Default,Man,0,0,0,,But, Lord Silat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:23.62,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:27.87,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,This mission is critical for restoring \Nour Bakiraka Clan's honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.87,0:16:33.38,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten our clan's \Ncenturies of torment in exile?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.96,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,This is our one and only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.39,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,Capture him before their main forces arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:39.89,Default,Silat,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:47.94,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.81,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Their ranks here have thinned!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:51.23,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,Lady Farnese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.07,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Why are you two bumbling around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.09,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Where are Elaine and the swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.35,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Don't tell me they're still back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.38,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:21.35,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Haven't you had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:23.35,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Shut up! Privates can stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.88,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,What'd you say, brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.11,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Even the main Kushan forces are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.62,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,They haven't noticed us yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.80,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:43.44,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,You're leaving those two behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.17,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,What choice do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:46.87,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,If we don't, we'll die for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.70,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:53.58,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:12.15,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:17.18,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,He isn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.78,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Do we ever get a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.53,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:28.83,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,He made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.84,Default,Ser,0,0,0,,But against such a large army...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:32.71,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,He'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:35.84,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll protect Elaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:38.59,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,He'd better not die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:41.47,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I'm gonna collect what he owes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.60,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Idiot! Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.18,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:54.36,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,There were other survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:57.56,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Everyone who fled into the tower died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:02.07,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,And those of little faith who fled \Nfrom the tower survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:06.37,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,I bet none of them will ever \Nfeel like praying again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:08.41,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:13.50,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Trying to survive is different \Nthan trying to run from fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.64,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,The survivors did what \Nthey had to do to live,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,without their surroundings interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:23.55,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I don't know what God thinks or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:29.05,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,but I believe He left humans enough \Nfree will to do what they need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.56,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Luca, what's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.90,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:35.34,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,It's for a chick that died in the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:40.27,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,It died without ever leaving the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:43.34,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Without meeting anyone or being known.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:48.12,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,A lonely one like that \Nsleeps beneath the rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:51.49,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I thought I should leave flowers for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:56.80,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,Any sinner should have at least \None person to mourn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:20:01.92,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,But if his wish came true,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.92,0:20:05.14,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,what will happen to the world now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:07.43,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Later, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:10.14,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I'm gonna bail! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.23,Default,Pepe,0,0,0,,As thanks, I'll be with you for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.15,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.60,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.40,Default,Ishi,0,0,0,,I'll take you up on it another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.69,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,They were a busy bunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:22.82,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Thankfully, they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.86,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I wonder if Elaine's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:28.57,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be fine with \Nthat black swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:31.58,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,He even fought Mozgus as an equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.29,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.75,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,The strength to protect someone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.75,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,is different than the strength \Nto be with someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:44.55,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,I need to take care of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:45.84,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:46.84,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:51.85,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.27,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Joachim...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:58.85,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,You're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.24,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,I've been wanting to apologize to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.78,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,For before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:09.36,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,I was so scared of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:12.61,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,I thought they'd kill me \Nif I didn't rat you out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:15.78,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,I know it's too late for me to say this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:18.29,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,but I really care for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:21.00,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,I really thought I could go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:24.28,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,But I didn't have the courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:26.00,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,so I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.14,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.26,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.38,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,W-Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:42.11,Default,Azan,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:45.81,Default,F,0,0,0,,I'm going to follow the Black Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.14,Default,F,0,0,0,,I am leaving the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.54,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:58.46,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,In the end, I could not escape \Nthe darkness of my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:04.26,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,Eventually, the darkness took shape \Nand appeared before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:10.26,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,As though the fate for one \Nwho continues to fear
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.39,0:22:13.81,Default - italics,F,0,0,0,,is to be led by the Black Swordsman
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:17.36,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,who stands alone in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:21.98,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,They left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.74,Default,Jer,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.49,0:22:28.41,Default - italics,Luca,0,0,0,,Hmm, Nina's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:29.95,Default,Pepe,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, introduce me to a noble patron, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:31.28,Default,Fuque,0,0,0,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:34.45,Default,Lucy,0,0,0,,Someone with more money \Nthan you, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.43,Default,Joa,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:42.76,Default,Nina,0,0,0,,Yeah, if I go back now, \NI won't be able to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.23,0:22:45.44,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.85,0:22:48.47,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm making you worry until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:51.84,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'm going with Joachim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.97,0:22:56.23,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I love you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:59.14,Default - italics,,0,0,0,,But if I stay with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.14,0:23:02.19,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I'll end up hating you again someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:04.78,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,And I'll hate myself, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:10.20,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,People who are strong will \Nend up hurting others,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:13.16,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,and people who are weak \Nwill end up hating others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:20.33,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,I think I'll go with this man, who has \Nthe same weakness and sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:26.67,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,If I'm with him, I think we can both \Nbecome a little stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:30.09,Default - italics,Nina,0,0,0,,And a little kinder.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:33.26,Default,FQ,0,0,0,,So slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:37.27,Default,Luca,0,0,0,,She really is such a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:42.81,Default - italics,Narr,0,0,0,,A rift appeared in the frontier that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.81,0:23:45.64,Default - italics,Narr,0,0,0,,Where the world's shape began to crumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:00.58,Title2 - Copy,Narr,0,0,0,,2017 Spring
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.50,0:24:06.80,Title2 - Copy,,0,0,0,,The Next Arc Arrives
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
